# Hero / section imagery
#
# Drop files in here and the components that expect them will pick them up.
# Expected slugs (referenced from src/pages/*.astro):
#
#   hero-phone.png        portrait phone mockup showing the HearthAI app —
#                         appears on the right side of the homepage hero
#
# Recommended specs for hero-phone.png:
#   - portrait orientation (~2:3 aspect ratio, e.g. 800x1200 or 1000x1500)
#   - transparent or white background preferred
#   - PNG or JPG, ideally under 400KB (run through tinypng.com or similar)
